OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FRail services on routes including
OL,8,FGreat Western Railway (GWR) and West
OL,9,FMidlands Trains were severely reduced
OL,10,Facross most parts of the country
OL,11,Fyesterday (16th June), as many train
OL,12,Fdrivers and other on-board staff
OL,13,Frefused to work overtime shifts on the
OL,14,Fday of England's opening Euro 2024
OL,15,Ffootball match.
OL,17,FNorthern, Great Western Railway and
OL,18,FLondon North Eastern Railway (LNER)
OL,19,Fall cancelled services scheduled to
OL,20,Frun on Sunday at short notice.
