OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FA rail industry source described
OL,8,FSunday as a "perfect storm" for poor
OL,9,Fstaff availability due England's match
OL,10,Fagainst Serbia, combined with it being
OL,11,FFather's Day and also the forecast of
OL,12,Fwarmer weather in many places.
OL,14,FPublicly-owned Northern issued a "do
OL,15,Fnot travel" alert at 4.42pm on Sunday
OL,16,Ffor its routes in north-west England
OL,17,Ffor the rest of the day.
