OL,3,CTrains cancelled as drivers refuse to
OL,4,Cwork extra shifts on day of England
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FIt said this was "due to the
OL,8,Funavailability of train crew", with
OL,9,Fmany late-night trains cancelled and
OL,10,Fno replacement buses provided.
OL,12,FMembers of train drivers' union Aslef
OL,13,Fare taking action short of a strike at
OL,14,FNorthern between 1st June and 27th
OL,15,FJuly, affecting availability of staff.
OL,17,FGWR warned passengers to expect "short-
OL,18,Fnotice cancellations and alterations"
OL,19,Fbecause of "a shortage of train crew".
